Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:37.42,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PASS THE MONSTER MEAT, MILADY!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:47.02,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KEKHAWATIRAN ADIPATI DARAH MENGAMUK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.02,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NYONYA LAFORGUE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.77,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NYONYA JOURDAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.36,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NYONYA SERREAU
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.50,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TIGA HARI KEMUDIAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:11.35,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 11: BUAH INI MANIS ATAU SEPAT,\NSCREAMWOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tak melepas perlengkapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasukan Elang Api masih berada di lokasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin akan kembali dengan temuan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mullan, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa, hanya saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah pintu bagian dalam\NKamar Tier ini terhubung
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan Kamar Ciel milik Nona Melphiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tak merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terlalu memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mullan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kau lihat\Npemimpin kawanan burung iblis itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski mereka burung iblis\Nyang berburu dalam kelompok,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}baru kali ini kulihat mereka\Nmengejar segigih ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berguignon terbesar itu\Npasti pemimpin mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku menyerbu ke dalam kawanan,\Nhanya ia yang tak menghindariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ia bahkan tak takut pada Naga Gletser?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu?\NApa ia sudah mengamuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan besar begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Mullan saja begitu yakin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berarti mungkin benar-benar telah mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung iblis bisa menelan Kristal Berawan\Nberenergi magis kuat tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ia mengamuk karena\Nakumulasi racun sihir berlebih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam kondisi itu, ia memimpin\Ndan membuat kawanannya lepas kendali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal jika berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Yang Mulia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebenarnya sejak kapan\NAnda kembangkan sihir sekejam itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi, aku sungguh mengira akan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mengaktifkan Formasi Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ide Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sihir yang dia pikirkan susah payah,\Nketerlaluan jika disebut kejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil sampingan penelitian Melphiera
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin cukup jadi senjata\Nyang menggemparkan negara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, itu tergantung cara memakainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sama sekali tidak salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi, yang bisa memahami\Ndan mengaktifkan Formasi Sihir ini
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin sangat sedikit di negara ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin melindungi Melphiera,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku butuh orang tepercaya untuk membantuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, orang seperti Mullan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, ada yang ingin kukatakan padamu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}soal "sihir kejam" yang kau sebut tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin dengar\Ntentang apa yang sebenarnya terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajudan Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa Anda memegang pedang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa suruh kau muncul mendadak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bikin kaget, bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pintu rahasia itu hanya\Nuntuk situasi darurat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia benar-benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, otak Anda yang darurat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Anda sudah bawa\NNona Melphiera ke Kamar Ciel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sengaja berputar dengan "akselerasi"\Ndan menunggu Anda di pintu utama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir aku harus mengatur akomodasi\Nuntuk Melphiera dulu, jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa masih perlu dikatakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi hal ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bergegas mencari pelayan\Nyang bisa melayani nona bangsawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kakak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tak seharusnya meninggalkan\NNona Melphiera sendirian di kamar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di medan perang, otak Anda\Nberputar lebih cepat dari siapa pun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi begitu bertemu hal begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda jadi sangat lambat.\NTolong sadar diri sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu senang sampai lupa diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin aku tinggalkan Melphiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah suruh\NPasukan Blanche mengikutinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasukan Blanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, mereka memang\Ncalon kesatria pengawal Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada salahnya\Nbiarkan mereka bertemu lebih awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Yang Mulia sudah terhitung lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon maaf, kalian jadi datang sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyonya Laforgue,\NNyonya Jourdan, Nyonya Serreau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya, sekarang Nona Melphiera
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sedang bertemu Pasukan Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kalian menunggu sebentar,\Nbaru mengantar gaun dan barang lainnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tak perlu minta maaf pada ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia hanya sedikit\Nterlalu senang sampai lupa diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga ingin segera\Nbertemu nona bangsawan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sangat dihargai Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar begitu, Mullan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh... ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum bertemu, mari duduk minum teh dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membawa daun teh bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari cicipi roti kami juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, ide bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paling suka teh hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada yang menyuruh\Nibu sendiri jadi pelayan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, dia orang paling kupercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi, dia pernah menjagamu saat kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kandidat terbaik\Nuntuk menjaga Nona Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha-Hal ini memang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, Ajudan Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa kakakku juga hadir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakku hanya membuka toko roti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena adiknya jadi kesatria,\Nkeluarga Nyonya Serreau tak ada pewaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia mencari suami untuk mewarisi\Nbisnis keluarga. Dia wanita hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakmu sungguh berjiwa besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh... benar, sungguh mengagumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan Nyonya Jourdan adalah\Nistri seorang kesatria Galbraith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kali ini hanya pengaturan mendadak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memilih ulang\Ndaftar nama resmi pelayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak keberatan dengan pilihan Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia selalu bisa melakukan sesuatu\Ndengan akurat tanpa celah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, ini sedikit menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lanjutkan topik tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkait sihir tadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tolong jelaskan semuanya dari awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir Anda hanya memiliki\Nenergi magis yang sangat dalam,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sebenarnya apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan Anda terobsesi\Ndengan Hutan Besar Erzenye
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai tubuh Anda jadi bagian dari hutan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julukan "Adipati Darah Mengamuk" mau\Ndiganti "Gunung Berapi Berjalan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya disebut\N"Pencipta Energi Magis" saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain kau, apa ada\Norang lain yang menyadarinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mullan, bagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sebenarnya tak terlalu paham\Napa yang sedang kalian bicarakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, saat itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang meledakkan\Nseluruh kawanan Berguignon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}disusun oleh Nona Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Melphiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang kejam itu ternyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ledakan sedahsyat itu adalah karyanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melphiera hanya membantuku\Nsekuat tenaganya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi, sihir itu juga menggunakan\Nenergi magis Zanas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Zanas yang kita makan saat sarapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melphiera menggambar semua Formasi Sihir\Nyang terpikirkan olehnya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di Kristal Berawan yang mengandung\Nenergi magis, lalu memberikannya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mengaktifkan Formasi Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin\Nbisa melakukan hal seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan Nona Melphiera itu genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, dia genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar jika Mullan merasa bingung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, arus utama sihir modern
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah pelafalan mantra yang disederhanakan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk meningkatkan efisiensi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan sihir kuno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya sisa legenda "kebijaksanaan\Npemberian peri di zaman mitos".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini, hampir tak ada\Nyang meneliti "sihir yang hilang".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hampir sepenuhnya\Nbelajar secara otodidak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sudah bisa menggambar\NFormasi Sihir skala itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kata Mullan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia memang genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau simpan data penelitian\NMelphiera dengan baik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, sudah kusimpan hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terutama Kristal Berawan dengan\Nenergi magis Moodle Agung,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah menyegelnya secara khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Energi magis itu bisa dipakai\Nuntuk tujuan damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum semua persiapan selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mullan, kau tak boleh bocorkan\Nyang kau dengar tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi, kenapa sengaja memberitahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenai ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin kau dan Pasukan Blanche\Nmenjadi pengawal Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanggung jawabmu sebagai\NKapten Pasukan Naga tetap berjalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi saat dibutuhkan,\Nkuharap kau bisa merangkap pengawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, bukankah Middlaeg sangat aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang keluar masuk terlalu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku siapkan ruang isolasi bekas\Nruang penelitiannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tetap harus berjaga-jaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan hentikan Melphiera\Nlanjutkan penelitiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika penelitiannya bisa menjadikan monster\Nsumber makanan yang aman,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Galbraith juga akan berkembang lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan hal ini padamu, Mullan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga harus bicarakan hal ini\Ndengan Melphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatinya terlalu baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin belum sadar penelitiannya\Nbisa dimanfaatkan orang jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, aku akan melindunginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang ingin kubahas dengan Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani sekali mengabaikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sedang kau katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda memakannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mata orang ini sama sekali tidak tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dijelaskan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Su-Sudah kubilang, aku tak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda makan Zanas nikmat\Nmasakan Nona Melphiera, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mullan, kau juga memakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang musim Zanas paling segar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian malah memakannya\Nselagi aku tak ada saat sarapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia, bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yang Mulia, maaf mengganggu.\N- Tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tidak bisa tenang.\N- Ajudan Chaos dan Kapten Mullan ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau sangat berbahaya seperti ini.\N- Ajudan Chaos dan Kapten Mullan ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku sangat ingin makan...\N- Ajudan Chaos dan Kapten Mullan ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku mengerti.\N- Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bisa begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasukan penyelidik melapor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagian Berguignon\Npunya tanda-tanda mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya begitu parah\Nsampai Anda harus bertindak sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah keseharian Galbraith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal hari ini aku ingin memperkenalkanmu\Nsecara resmi pada semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, baru sampai,\Nkau harus menghadapi hal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku juga bisa membantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tentu saja ingin tinggal di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi burung iblis yang mengamuk\Nbisa menyerang desa kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tunggu aku di sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengatasinya secepat mungkin,\Njangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti, Tuan Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah, Melphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seharusnya memanggilku apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:14:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke-Kenapa Tuan Aristide\Nselalu suka mempersulitku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}To-Tolong selesaikan penaklukan secepatnya,\Nlalu kembali dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bermaksud mempersulitmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mendadak berkata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melphie, ingat tanggung jawabmu\Nsebagai Nyonya Adipati?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus memperhatikan\Ndan menyembuhkan Tuan Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan sembuh\Nmelihat reaksimu yang imut begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon maklumi aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku kembali,\Nhibur aku dengan makanan nikmat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kupikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rebus saja sisa Moodle Agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa dimasak jadi hidangan biasa\Npun rasanya sangat bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal enak, apa pun boleh,\Nbahkan Berguignon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku jadi makin semangat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika berpikir\Naku pergi berburu bahan makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Adipati sengaja menekankan\Nbahwa dia juga ingin makan monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mengakui hidangan monster\Ndi depan Pasukan Blanche dan lainnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka akan lebih mudah\Nmenerima penelitianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memikirkan kebaikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada monster yang menarik bagimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa sekalian kutangkapkan untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sepertinya tak tahu malu\Njika meminta monster besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, dia akan pergi\Nmenaklukkan Berguignon yang mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia sudah berkata begitu,\Nsebaiknya kuterima kebaikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin buah Screamwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat itu salah satu monster\Nyang Anda sesali setelah mencicipinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uh, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar baunya menyengat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Tuan Mullan sepertinya\Nmerasa itu lebih nikmat dari madu buah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Melphiera, kenapa Anda tahu soal ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rahasia sesama perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mullan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau makan memang buah Screamwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena terlalu matang,\Njadi seluruh buahnya hitam,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aromanya sangat pekat dan manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti kebahagiaan\Nyang meleleh di mulut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, aku tak sengaja\Nmakan terlalu banyak
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai Air Pemurni pun tak bisa menolongku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasi setelah itu\Nsungguh tak ingin kuingat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal jenis buahnya sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa penilaian setiap orang\Nbisa berbeda jauh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh membuat penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau memang bisa sekalian, bawa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang terpenting Tuan Adipati\Ndan lainnya kembali dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika melihatnya, akan kubawa pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selagi belum gelap,\Nmari berangkat ke benteng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap ini bayaran di muka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Data penelitianmu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah dipindah ke kamar yang dulu kupakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Blanche, antar dia ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Aristide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda harus kembali dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Nona Melphiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Anda tak tidur nyenyak semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung iblis yang menyerang kemarin\Nsudah cukup merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlebih burung iblis yang mengamuk,\Nmemikirkannya membuatku tak bisa tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sempat terpikir meledakkan Kristal Berawan\Nmungkin bisa membasmi semua burung iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi hanya tersisa Kristal Berawan\Ndengan energi magis Moodle Agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Energi magis kristal itu sangat kuat\Ndan jumlahnya tak sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika diledakkan, mungkin\Nakan melukai Tuan Adipati dan lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya bisa menunggu\Nsungguh membuat gelisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah, Yang Mulia akan segera kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, mari sarapan dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda harus menyambut kepulangan\NYang Mulia dengan senyuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia menyuruhku membawa Anda ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ruang penelitian\Nyang bisa Anda gunakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengejutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya data penelitianku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada juga buku sihir dan literatur\Nyang terlihat menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, entah kenapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sama sekali tak tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alhasil, setelah hari berakhir,\NTuan Adipati belum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Adipati!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah Anda baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membuatmu menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berkata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawa oleh-oleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutemukan sesuatu yang menarik di hutan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga buah Screamwood yang kau inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti diantar ke kamarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sebelum itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus tidur sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Adipati?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini oleh-oleh Tuan Adipati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buah Screamwood yang legendaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang dimakan Tuan Adipati dulu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti buah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di ilustrasi tertulis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buah Screamwood berwarna merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baunya menyengat dan rasanya sangat sepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, letakkan buah merah ini\Ndi luar dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cairan bersinar itu energi magis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini benar-benar sulit\Nmencabut energi magisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tak sempat menjawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pohon iblis tak sepenuhnya layu\Natau dibakar jadi abu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ia tak bisa benar-benar mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, begitu pohon layu,\Nbuahnya tak bisa dimakan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit sekali mencabut\Nenergi magisnya saat masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak disangka, setelah energi magis dicabut,\Nbuahnya jadi begitu wangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa berbeda dengan yang pernah\Nkalian makan, Kapten?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata "bau" sama sekali tak bisa\Ngambarkan aroma sekuat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, warna buahnya\Ndulu tak sehitam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat mirip buah\Nyang diletakkan di luar tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kita tertipu penampilan luarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kulit hitam pekat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sungguh tak membangkitkan selera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aromanya justru membuat ingin menggigitnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wangi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Buah Ini Manis atau Sepat".
